eed 20km per hour. These fastenings must be shown in the following manner:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) A red piece of cloth measuring a minimum 0.50m by side\",\"b\":\"b) An orange-colored light laterally visible\",\"c\":\"c) A square white panel of at least 0.20m by side\",\"d\":\"d) None of these is the answer\"},\"userAnswer\":\"d) None of these is the answer\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"correctAnswer\":\"d) None of these is the answer\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"isCorrect\":true,\"points\":1,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q18\",\"questionText\":\"With exception to urban areas, on the other roads as determined by the minister having transport in his duties, the maximum weights authorized for three and more axle vehicles excepting semi-trailers is:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) 10 tonnes\",\"b\":\"b) 12 tonnes\",\"c\":\"c) 16 tonnes\",\"d\":\"d) 24 tonnes\"},\"userAnswer\":\"c) 16 tonnes\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"correctAnswer\":\"c) 16 tonnes\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"isCorrect\":true,\"points\":1,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q19\",\"questionText\":\"The width of the loading on tricycles and quadricycles with or without an engine and trailers pulled by these vehicles cannot exceed:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) by more than 0.30m on the width of the vehicle when not loaded\",\"b\":\"b) Absolute maximum width is 2.50m\",\"c\":\"c) A and B are both correct\",\"d\":\"d) None of the answers is correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"c) A and B are both correct\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"correctAnswer\":\"c) A and B are both correct\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"isCorrect\":true,\"points\":1,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q2\",\"questionText\":\"The brake light of red color must be visible in clear weather at a minimum distance of:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) 100 m by day light and 20 meters at night\",\"b\":\"b) 150 m by day light and 50 meters at night\",\"c\":\"c) 200 m by day light and 100 meters at night\",\"d\":\"d) None of them are correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"c) 200 m by day light and 100 meters at night\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"correctAnswer\":\"d) None of them are correct\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"isCorrect\":false,\"points\":0,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q20\",\"questionText\":\"Overtaking any other vehicle than a two-wheeled vehicle is forbidden:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) Near a bridge, with a narrow roadway\",\"b\":\"b) Near a passage for pedestrians\",\"c\":\"c) Near parts of dangerous roads.\",\"d\":\"d) All answers are correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"b) Near a passage for pedestrians\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"b\",\"correctAnswer\":\"d) All answers are correct\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"isCorrect\":false,\"points\":0,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q3\",\"questionText\":\"When the speed of unloaded vehicles on a flat surface cannot exceed 50km per hour, the sounding alarm apparatus can be heard at a distance of:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) 50 m\",\"b\":\"b) 200 m\",\"c\":\"c) 100 m\",\"d\":\"d) 150 m\"},\"userAnswer\":\"c) 100 m\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"correctAnswer\":\"a) 50 m\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"a\",\"isCorrect\":false,\"points\":0,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q4\",\"questionText\":\"The circulation of self-propelling vehicles and trailers pulled by these vehicles is forbidden when their wheels are provided with either rigid bandages or elastic bandages of less than 0.04 meter thick. But this provision does not apply to:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) Military vehicles when they are in traffic within a maximum radius of 25 km\",\"b\":\"b) Agricultural vehicles\",\"c\":\"c) Vehicles of national police\",\"d\":\"d) None of them is correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"d) None of them is correct\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"correctAnswer\":\"d) None of them is correct\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"isCorrect\":true,\"points\":1,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q5\",\"questionText\":\"The section of the public highway delineated by two broken and parallel white lines, and not wide enough for automobile vehicles traffic constitutes:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) Bicycles and mopeds\",\"b\":\"b) The wheel barrows\",\"c\":\"c) Cycles\",\"d\":\"d) None of them is correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"d) None of them is correct\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"correctAnswer\":\"c) Cycles\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"isCorrect\":false,\"points\":0,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q6\",\"questionText\":\"The width of trailer is limited to the width of the hauling vehicle when the trailer is pulled by:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) A bicycle\",\"b\":\"b) A scooter\",\"c\":\"c) A motorcycle with sidecar\",\"d\":\"d) All answers are correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"c) A motorcycle with sidecar\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"correctAnswer\":\"d) All answers are correct\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"isCorrect\":false,\"points\":0,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q7\",\"questionText\":\"When the other seats are not available in the car, it is forbidden to carry on the front seat children of less than:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) 12 years\",\"b\":\"b) 10 years\",\"c\":\"c) 7 years\",\"d\":\"d) None of them is correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"c) 7 years\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"correctAnswer\":\"a) 12 years\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"a\",\"isCorrect\":false,\"points\":0,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q8\",\"questionText\":\"The sign which indicates the right of way before vehicles coming in the opposite direction has the following colors:\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a) White surface\",\"b\":\"b) Symbol is red and black\",\"c\":\"c) Symbol is black\",\"d\":\"d) None of the answers is correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"d) None of the answers is correct\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"correctAnswer\":\"d) None of the answers is correct\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"d\",\"isCorrect\":true,\"points\":1,\"questionImgUrl\":null},{\"questionId\":\"2_q9\",\"questionText\