2_q11\",\"questionText\":\"At this junction, there’s a ‘stop’ sign and a solid white line on the road surface. Why is there a ‘stop’ sign here?\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a. Speed on the major road is derestricted\",\"b\":\"b. It’s a busy junction\",\"c\":\"c. Visibility along the major road-way is limited\",\"d\":\"d. There are hazard warning lines in the center of the road\"},\"userAnswer\":\"a. Speed on the major road is derestricted\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"a\",\"correctAnswer\":\"c. Visibility along the major road-way is limited\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"c\",\"isCorrect\":false,\"points\":0,\"questionImgUrl\":\"/uploads/question-images/q261.png\"},{\"questionId\":\"12_q12\",\"questionText\":\"Which of these is needed before you can legally use a vehicle on the road?\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a. A valid driving license, Proper insurance and Motor-vehicle certificate\",\"b\":\"b. Identity certificate\",\"c\":\"c. Proper insurance\",\"d\":\"d. None of the answers is correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"a. A valid driving license, Proper insurance and Motor-vehicle certificate\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"a\",\"correctAnswer\":\"a. A valid driving license, Proper insurance and Motor-vehicle certificate\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"a\",\"isCorrect\":true,\"points\":1,\"questionImgUrl\":\"\"},{\"questionId\":\"12_q13\",\"questionText\":\"A new vehicle will need its first Motor-vehicle inspection test when it’s how old?\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a. After One year\",\"b\":\"b. After Two years\",\"c\":\"c. A and B are correct\",\"d\":\"d. None of the answers is correct\"},\"userAnswer\":\"a. After One year\",\"userAnswerLetter\":\"a\",\"correctAnswer\":\"b. After Two years\",\"correctAnswerLetter\":\"b\",\"isCorrect\":false,\"points\":0,\"questionImgUrl\":\"\"},{\"questionId\":\"12_q14\",\"questionText\":\"When should you use simultaneously all the vehicle’s indicators lights?\",\"options\":{\"a\":\"a. When you want to warn other road users\",\"b\":\"b. When your vehicle is causing a tempora