('10_q18', '10', 'Why should you always reduce your speed when travelling in fog?', 'a. The brakes don’t work as well', 'b. You’ll be dazzled by other headlights', 'c. It’s more difficult to see what’s ahead', 'd. The engine will take longer to warm up', 'c. It’s more difficult to see what’s ahead', 1, '', '2025-09-25 12:42:09', '2025-09-27 10:28:36', 18),
